== Wut Had Happened Wuz ==

[[Image:Pyramid_scheme.jpg|thumb|right|How he did it]] 
Bernie Madoff founded an investment company in 1960 called Bernard L. Madoff Investment Securities, LLC. They took [[celebrity|peoples']] money, invested it for them, and all was well. Then [[USA|someone]] [[Terri_Schiavo|pwned]] the stock market and when people went for withdrawals from Madoff's investment company there were no funds to be had. In response to an unprecedented outcry by the severely butthurt [[jews|investors]] Madoff is currently awaiting trial in a swanky penthouse somewhere in [[New York|Jew York's]] upper east side.


